item.title: Turkish Lira Falls as Erdogan Wins Presidential Election
item.description: The Turkish lira fell after Erdogan’s win in Sunday’s runoff presidential election, as his controversial policy of keeping interest rates low has put pressure on the currency and will likely continue to do so, UniCredit said.
